title: New Tai-Hao Cubic Alps-mount keycaps review

media:group.media:title: New Tai-Hao Cubic Alps-mount keycaps review
media:group.media:description:
Erratum; this set is actually NOT fully compatible with the AEK, which uses rotated switches and extended key posts for the F keys. Thanks to poip032 for reminding me!
Get them here: https://shop.tai-hao.com/categories/alps-keycaps
Man, this turned out to be WAY more work than I thought it would be xD . 
Today we look at one of Tai-Hao's new Alps-mount keycap sets! Choices for Alps keycaps are quite limited, so these new (and expanded) sets are a very interesting new arrival! Hope you enjoy the video!
